text: She has subsequently admitted the existence of the conversation and offered an explanation for her denial.
transcription_expl: ʃˑˈi hˈæz s˘ˈʌbs˘əkwən˘t˘l˘i əˑdmˑˈɪt˘ɪˑd ðəˑ ɛ˘ɡˑz˘ˈɪˑs˘təns˘ ˈʌv ðə kˌɑn˘v˘ər˘sˈeɪʃəˑnˑ əːnd ˈɔfər˘d ˈæ˘n ˌɛks˘pl˘ənˈeɪʃə˘n fˈɔr hˈʌr dɪnˈaɪəˑlˑ.
